  </row>
  <row>
    <entry valign="top"><emphasis effect="bold">Step 3. Name</emphasis> what we are looking for.</entry>
    <entry valign="top">Let <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> the number of adult tickets.<newline/><m:math><m:mrow><m:mspace width="1.5em"/><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> the number of child tickets</entry>
  </row>
