</entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry valign="top">The number times the value gives the total<newline/>value, so the total value of adult tickets is<newline/><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, and the total value of child<newline/>tickets is <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></entry>
