  </row>
  <row>
    <entry valign="top"><emphasis effect="bold">Step 5. Check</emphasis> the answer in the problem.<newline/><newline/>  42 adult tickets at $11 per ticket makes $462<newline/>  105 child tickets at $8 per ticket makes $840.<newline/>  The total receipts are $1,302.✓</entry>
    <entry/>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry valign="top"><emphasis effect="bold">Step 6. Answer</emphasis> the question.</entry>
    <entry valign="top">The movie theater sold 42 adult tickets and 105 child tickets.</entry>
  </row>
