    <entry valign="top">The value of each nickel is $0.05.<newline/>The value of each quarter is $0.25.</entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry valign="top">The number times the value gives the total<newline/>value, so, the total value of the nickels is<newline/><emphasis effect="italics">n</emphasis> (0.05) = 0.05<emphasis effect="italics">n</emphasis> and the total value of<newline/>quarters is <emphasis effect="italics">q</emphasis>(0.25) = 0.25<emphasis effect="italics">q</emphasis>.<newline/>Altogether the total value of the coins<newline/>is $7.30.</entry>
   <entry valign="top"><media id="fs-id1167829624601" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_05_05_002a_img_new.jpg"/></media></entry>
