   <entry valign="top"><media id="fs-id1167829811989" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_05_05_002b_img_new.jpg"/></media></entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry valign="top">We also know the number of nickels is six less<newline/>than three times the number of quarters.<newline/>Translate to get the second equation.</entry>
   <entry valign="bottom"><media id="fs-id1167836321903" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_05_05_002c_img_new.jpg"/></media></entry>
  </row>
  <row>
